        <div class="container footer-container">

          <div class="footer-left">
            <div class="footer-name">
              <img src="24b21208c1893f5fd07645c61e23e110" alt=""> <h4>Cole Caccamise</h4>
            </div>

            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. At quibusdam nemo sapiente ut, quis inventore enim doloribus quidem nam ea. Et possimus inventore minima.</p>

